Saṃyutta Nikāya 13 
1. Abhisamayavagga 
4. Dutiyasambhejjaudakasutta 
Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. 
“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yatthimā mahānadiyo saṃsandanti samenti, seyyathidaṃ—
